Title: Lisbeth Salander
Running time: approx 3 hours 10 minutes

An edit and combination of all three Millennium trilogy films:
The Girl With The Dragon Tattoo
The Girl Who Played With Fire
The Girl Who Kicked The Hornet's Nest
all edited together into one film and focusing on Lisbeth over all other characters.

A must have for die-hard fans!!!
